holy shit this guy is a fucking dumbshit. i can hardly believe my eyes when i read his fucking stupid ass words. getting all nostalgic and shit when it aint even over yet. u ass fucker. u are so into urself as u are all like yeah ima get a ugly piece of shit dodge ram with a 5.9. its like shut the fuck up man. i doubt anyone gives a rats ass about ur pathetic...computer programmed life dude. u are fucking worthless man. all talking like "yeah im hella slart. ima miss my hometown and shit oh yeah and im going to 20 parties for graduation cause i got nothin better to do than to waste it all at a fucking party...and then college is gonna be so cool and im a fuckin flamer ass bitch" holy fuck man. you didnt even DO anything to me and i am still hating you just because you are unbelievably ignorant.

dont u realize what u fucking write? u try to speak all intellectually and such...but ur wording sucks ass. yeah no shit i swear a lot and i mispell but its the fucking internet man if i wanted to write a 1st class essay, i would shit all over you and wipe my ass with whatever the fuck u called an essay. ur one sad mother fucker man and u got my complete and utter pity. i just cant stand arrogant people. u think ur the shit, but i can chop you right down bitch. UN-fuckin believable. im like trippin hella bad....i have never seen nor heard of a DUMB FUCK as bad as you are man. ur one pathetic mutha fucka.

he lives his life under a blanket of stereotypes and ego. how into oneself can a human be? it is almost overwhelmingly disgusting. life is not about statistics and probablility. it is not about calculation or accomplishments. it is about waking up each fucking morning going out into the world...and living, breathing, conversing. being human is what life is all about. many people do not grasp this concept and i have great pity for them. PITY i say. fucking disgrace.
